e-up_0.8s_ease-out_both]\" data-kid=\"24\">\n            <div class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-3 px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-md mb-8 shimmer-border\" data-kid=\"25\">\n                <span class=\"flex h-2 w-2 relative\" data-kid=\"26\">\n                    <span class=\"animate-ping absolute inline-flex h-full w-full rounded-full bg-amber-400 opacity-75\" data-kid=\"27\"></span>\n                    <span class=\"relative inline-flex rounded-full h-2 w-2 bg-amber-500\" data-kid=\"28\"></span>\n                </span>\n                <span class=\"text-[10px] font-mono font-semibold text-amber-100/90 uppercase tracking-[0.25em]\" data-kid=\"29\">VERSION 4.2 PRO • CINEMATIC RELEASE</span>\n            </div>\n\n            <h1 class=\"text-white text-[105px] font-display font-black leading-[0.82] tracking-[-0.05em] mb-6\" data-kid=\"30\">\n                THE TEAM OS <br data-kid=\"31\">\n                <span class=\"gold-text-gradient italic font-extrabold pr-4 tracking-[-0.02em]\" data-kid=\"32\">EDUTECHEX</span> <br data-kid=\"33\">\n                RUNS ON.\n            </h1>\n\n            <p class=\"text-slate-400 text-xl leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mb-12\" data-kid=\"34\">\n                All the context your team needs — channels, embedded AI, auto-extracted tasks, and morning digests — without the noise.\n            </p>\n\n            \n            <div class=\"flex items-center gap-8 mb-20\" data-kid=\"35\">\n                <button class=\"group relative px-12 py-5 bg-amber-400 rounded-sm overflow-hidden transition-all hover:scale-105 shadow-[0_10px_50px_-10px_rgba(251,191,36,0.6)]\" data-kid=\"36\">\n                    <div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-white/30 translate-x-[-150%] group-hover:translate-x-[150%] transition-transform duration-1000 ease-in-out\" data-kid=\"37\"></div>\n                    <span class=\"relative text-black font-black tracking-[0.2em] text-[10px] flex items-center gap-3\" d